248
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:47,740
Don't use a shaver.

249
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:49,740
Just use scissors.

250
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:51,020
Every time I look up,

251
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:52,780
