I can fight them.

294
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:23,700
Fighting is not okay.

295
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:26,100
Call the police if you're in trouble.

296
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:27,580
Don't fight them yourself.

297
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:28,620
Besides,

298
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:29,900
you can call me Bei.

299
00:16:29,940 --> 00:16:30,940
No need for formalities.

300
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:32,340
Okay.

301
00:16:33,180 --> 00:16:35,540
When I'm older,
I'll come to you for lessons.

302
00:16:35,740 --> 00:16:36,460
No problem.

303
00:16:37,740 --> 00:16:38,540
Officer Zheng,

304
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:40,740
thank you so much.

305
00:16:40,780 --> 00:16:42,340
If something had happened to Mao,

306
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:44,580
I wouldn't be able to face my sister.

307
00:16:44,900 --> 00:16:45,860
You saved both her

308
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:46,780
and me.

309
00:16:47,100 --> 00:16:47,900
How about this?

310
00:16:48,180 --> 00:16:50,620
I'll call you Bei too.

311
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:52,500
Because she calls me that?

312
00:16:52,900 --> 00:16:53,580
Fine.

313
00:16:53,620 --> 00:16:55,460
As long as you don't mind.

314
00:16:55,860 --> 00:16:57,140
Alright. I'll call you Bei then.

315
00:16:57,260 --> 00:16:57,900
Okay.

316
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:59,660
Dinner is ready. Let's eat.

317
00:16:59,780 --> 00:17:00,780
- OK.
- Come on, Bei.

318
00:17:00,820 --> 00:17:01,420
Let's go eat.

319
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:02,220
Please sit here.

320
00:17:04,100 --> 00:17:04,820
Thank you, Bei.

321
00:17:04,900 --> 00:17:05,980
You're welcome.

322
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:06,940
That's my duty.

323
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:11,980
Officer Zheng,

324
00:17:13,060 --> 00:17:15,300
I can't thank you enough.

325
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:16,860
If it weren't for you,

326
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:17,540
that knife would have

327
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:19,180
landed on Mao.

328
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:21,020
If something had happened to her,

329
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:23,060
I wouldn't be able

330
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:25,020
to live anymore.

331
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:28,020
I'm fine.

332
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:29,860
Don't scare yourself.

333
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:31,940
What a good kid.

334
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:32,940
It's okay.

335
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:34,340
Look at this big sausage.

336
00:17:34,460 --> 00:17:36,100
I'll recover soon after eating it.

337
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:38,460
Oh, I'm making turtle soup.

338
00:17:38,580 --> 00:17:39,100
Let me bring it over.

339
00:17:39,180 --> 00:17:40,420
Xiaohai, look after him.
You guys eat.

340
00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:41,220
More dishes?

341
00:17:41,220 --> 00:17:41,980
What a feast.

342
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:42,460
Just eat.

343
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:43,580
Let's eat, Bei.

344
00:17:43,660 --> 00:17:44,460
Okay.

345
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:52,460
I need light.

346
00:18:11,180 --> 00:18:12,380
Come on.

347
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:15,700
The candle is burning out.

348
00:18:18,460 --> 00:18:20,780
No wonder people like candlelit dinner.

349
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:22,780
You look so pretty

350
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:24,860
in candle light.

351
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:29,300
Like your long-lost ancestor?

352
00:18:30,340 --> 00:18:31,140
Hurry up.

353
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:33,300
My brother could have fixed it
in a minute.

354
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:34,300
Alright.

355
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:44,540
It's fixed.

356
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:51,220
Are you stupid?

357
00:18:51,260 --> 00:18:52,260
I'll get you some medicine.

358
00:18:52,300 --> 00:18:53,100
No.

359
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:54,420
I don't need it.

360
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:56,220
It doesn't hurt at all.

361
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,180
Well.

362
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:02,860
How about we turn off the light

363
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:05,420
and have a candlelit dinner?

364
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:07,140
I'll buy you sweet and sour pork.

365
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:11,060
Candlelit dinners are all about
fancy Western food.

366
00:19:11,140 --> 00:19:13,140
Who has sweet and sour pork?

367
00:19:13,260 --> 00:19:14,420
Besides,

368
00:19:14,860 --> 00:19:16,620
a romantic dinner

369
00:19:17,100 --> 00:19:19,420
has to be eaten with Prince Charming.

370
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:21,820
You and I...

371
00:19:22,300 --> 00:19:23,380
Why bother?

372
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:26,180
Let's go out and eat.

373
00:19:26,300 --> 00:19:27,620
I want to eat pork kidney.

374
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,340
Well, look closely.

375
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:31,100
Do I not look like a prince
in candle light?

376
00:19:31,220 --> 00:19:32,980
Look at me.

377
00:19:41,900 --> 00:19:43,780
Taste this sausage.

378
00:19:44,020 --> 00:19:44,980
Officer Zheng.

379
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:46,500
You're back.

380
00:19:48,100 --> 00:19:48,580
Your brother-in-law?

381
00:19:48,620 --> 00:19:49,380
Yes.

382
00:19:49,660 --> 00:19:50,460
Nice to meet you.

383
00:19:51,180 --> 00:19:52,140
Please sit down, Officer Zheng.

384
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:52,820
Officer Zheng.

385
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:54,100
Officer Zheng.

386
00:19:54,740 --> 00:19:56,860
Thank you so much

387
00:19:57,260 --> 00:19:57,900
for today.

388
00:19:58,020 --> 00:19:58,540
That's my duty.

389
00:19:58,660 --> 00:19:59,180
You're welcome.

390
00:19:59,220 --> 00:20:00,420
I came to eat for free.

391
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:01,700
Don't say that.

392
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:03,100
If you like,

393
00:20:03,260 --> 00:20:04,780
you can come at any time.

394
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:06,260
Take a seat.

395
00:20:06,340 --> 00:20:07,220
Let's sit and chat.

396
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:09,660
Mao.

397
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:12,020
Your old roller skates broke.

398
00:20:12,260 --> 00:20:13,380
I bought you new ones.

399
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:14,620
Do you like them?

400
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:15,580
Thanks.

401
00:20:17,820 --> 00:20:18,420
Officer Zheng.

402
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:19,620
I'm not very good

403
00:20:19,700 --> 00:20:21,300
with words.

404
00:20:23,620 --> 00:20:24,980
This is a small gift.

405
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:26,060
Please take it.

406
00:20:26,100 --> 00:20:28,100
No, I can't.

407
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:29,060
We have rules.

408
00:20:29,180 --> 00:20:30,300
I can't break the rules.

409
00:20:30,620 --> 00:20:31,620
Please keep it. I can't.

410
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:34,500
Bei is a police officer.

411
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:35,900
He didn't save Mao for this.

412
00:20:36,060 --> 00:20:37,380
Don't make things difficult for him.

413
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:41,020
Sorry, I was thoughtless.

414
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:42,900
Well, Officer Zheng.

415
00:20:43,020 --> 00:20:44,420
Let me know

416
00:20:44,740 --> 00:20:45,420
if you need anything.

417
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,140
Yingzi runs a pharmacy.

418
00:20:47,340 --> 00:20:49,860
Just let her know
if you need any supplements.

419
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:50,580
Okay.

420
00:20:50,660 --> 00:20:51,100
No need to be polite.

421
00:20:51,460 --> 00:20:52,940
Yes. Come at any time.

422
00:20:52,980 --> 00:20:53,780
Alright.

423
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:56,020
Don't mind me.

424
00:20:57,460 --> 00:20:58,300
Eat it, Bei.

425
00:20:59,540 --> 00:21:00,420
Let's wait for him.

426
00:21:00,620 --> 00:21:01,180
It's okay.

427
00:21:01,180 --> 00:21:02,180
Yingzi.

428
00:21:02,380 --> 00:21:02,940
Look.

429
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:04,780
Your old one's almost gone.

430
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:05,860
The sales clerk said

431
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:07,740
this is the hottest color of the year.

432
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:09,220
It's too red.

433
00:21:09,340 --> 00:21:10,260
It's for young girls.

434
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:11,500
It's okay. It suits you.

435
00:21:11,620 --> 00:21:12,980
They are so affectionate.

436
00:21:13,140 --> 00:21:13,940
Yes.

437
00:21:14,580 --> 00:21:15,820
They never brought me

438
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:16,580
on their family trips.

439
00:21:16,780 --> 00:21:18,180
Are you speaking ill of me?

440
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:19,180
No.

441
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:20,500
Here is turtle soup.

442
00:21:20,700 --> 00:21:22,340
The main dish arrived.

443
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:24,420
Officer Zheng.

444
00:21:24,820 --> 00:21:25,500
Let me serve you some.

445
00:21:25,540 --> 00:21:26,020
I can do it myself.

446
00:21:26,060 --> 00:21:26,540
I'll help you.

447
00:21:26,620 --> 00:21:27,260
Let me tell you.

448
00:21:27,300 --> 00:21:30,260
The real deal in this soup
is the turtle's calipash.

449
00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:31,900
They're fresh, tender,

450
00:21:31,940 --> 00:21:33,180
and packed with nutrients.

451
00:21:33,220 --> 00:21:34,140
Try it. Have more.

452
00:21:34,140 --> 00:21:34,780
Okay, thanks.

453
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:35,500
Try some.

454
00:21:35,580 --> 00:21:36,260
Come on.

455
00:21:36,940 --> 00:21:37,540
Let me do it.

456
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:38,260
It's okay.

457
00:21:38,740 --> 00:21:39,300
Yummy.

458
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:40,380
Does it taste good?

459
00:21:40,620 --> 00:21:40,980
Yes.

460
00:21:41,260 --> 00:21:41,940
Eat more.

461
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:43,620
Here you go.

462
00:21:45,100 --> 00:21:46,180
This is yours.

463
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:47,460
Bei, you guys eat.

464
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:48,460
I'll make a call.

465
00:21:48,660 --> 00:21:49,140
Okay.

466
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:51,100
Can you pass?

467
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:00,940
Yingzi.

468
00:22:01,660 --> 00:22:03,020
Do you know some first aid

469
00:22:03,180 --> 00:22:05,980
running a pharmacy?

470
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:07,060
Yes.

471
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:08,460
Sometimes our neighbor

472
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:10,300
had a headache, fever, or injuries,

473
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:11,740
he would ask me for help.

474
00:22:12,820 --> 00:22:16,140
Xiaohai gave me the tobacco

475
00:22:16,300 --> 00:22:17,940
to stop bleeding.

476
00:22:18,220 --> 00:22:19,380
It's nice.

477
00:22:19,620 --> 00:22:20,740
How does it work?

478
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:21,860
This brat

479
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:23,460
finally remembers something useful.

480
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:24,260
You don't know

481
00:22:24,300 --> 00:22:25,300
how naughty he was as a kid.

482
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:27,140
He hurt himself every day.

483
00:22:27,260 --> 00:22:28,060
At that time,

484
00:22:28,260 --> 00:22:30,180
I used my dad's tobacco
to stop his bleeding.

485
00:22:30,380 --> 00:22:31,940
It's a folk recipe for first aid.

486
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:06,500
Why don't you go home?

487
00:23:06,540 --> 00:23:07,420
What are you doing?

488
00:23:09,380 --> 00:23:10,660
I'm thinking of revising

489
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:12,140
tomorrow's lesson plan

490
00:23:13,060 --> 00:23:15,100
to make it vivid

491
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:16,900
and engaging.

492
00:23:17,620 --> 00:23:18,820
I'm having trouble understanding it.

493
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,260
What are you back for?

494
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:23,940
Just to grab a key.

495
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:31,740
Did you find anything

496
00:23:33,220 --> 00:23:34,420
on your home visit?

497
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:36,860
At first, I was suspicious of Xiaohai.

498
00:23:36,940 --> 00:23:39,860
He knows some street-smart tricks.

499
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:42,620
When I looked into it,

500
00:23:42,900 --> 00:23:44,100
I found out...

501
00:23:45,940 --> 00:23:47,740
his sister taught him
since he was little.

502
00:23:48,860 --> 00:23:49,820
I thought too much.

503
00:23:50,820 --> 00:23:52,420
A good police

504
00:23:53,220 --> 00:23:54,940
keeps an eye on everything suspicious.

505
00:23:56,540 --> 00:23:58,300
That makes sense.

506
00:24:06,980 --> 00:24:07,780
Mr. Gu.

507
00:24:08,900 --> 00:24:10,060
Let me ask you.

508
00:24:10,780 --> 00:24:12,460
Your personality is

509
00:24:13,900 --> 00:24:14,820
really something.

510
00:24:15,580 --> 00:24:17,060
On the one hand,

511
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:19,460
you can be pretty sharp with your words.

512
00:24:20,180 --> 00:24:21,820
On the other hand,

513
00:24:22,300 --> 00:24:24,100
you take teasing from everyone

514
00:24:24,500 --> 00:24:26,060
with a smile.

515
00:24:26,820 --> 00:24:27,660
Xiaoguang and the others said

516
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:29,660
you gave them one class after another

517
00:24:29,980 --> 00:24:31,860
to torture them.

518
00:24:32,020 --> 00:24:33,740
However, you were making teaching plans

519
00:24:34,140 --> 00:24:35,900
after work.

520
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:37,500
This is fun.

521
00:24:41,420 --> 00:24:42,660
I came to Halan

522
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:44,900
to assist you guys.

523
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:47,500
This is my duty.

524
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:52,580
Mr. Gu.

525
00:24:53,260 --> 00:24:54,060
Tell me.

526
00:24:55,660 --> 00:24:56,900
Have you ever been upset

527
00:24:57,940 --> 00:25:00,180
like other normal guys?

528
00:25:11,900 --> 00:25:13,180
Time will tell.

529
00:25:13,940 --> 00:25:15,020
Sooner or later,

530
00:25:16,020 --> 00:25:17,500
the special investigation team
will accept me.

531
00:25:19,580 --> 00:25:21,660
Wow, you're really on another level.

532
00:25:22,300 --> 00:25:23,940
Can't get anything out of your mouth.

533
00:25:34,060 --> 00:25:35,620
Mouse sent a message.

534
00:25:35,780 --> 00:25:36,900
That guy

535
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:39,500
will sell drugs at a club today.

536
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:41,460
He didn't say what the guy looked like.

537
00:25:42,500 --> 00:25:43,820
Be smart

538
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:44,660
when you observe the crowd.

539
00:25:44,740 --> 00:25:46,380
If you find anyone suspicious,

540
00:25:46,860 --> 00:25:48,500
lure them away from the crowd
before catching them.

541
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:49,940
Don't alert other people.

542
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:50,980
Got it.

543
00:25:53,660 --> 00:25:56,020
Bei, are we not going
to catch the suspect?

544
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:57,820
Mr. Gu can't fight.

545
00:25:57,940 --> 00:25:59,500
Why is he with us?

546
00:26:00,660 --> 00:26:02,220
We act as a group.

547
00:26:02,900 --> 00:26:03,980
Mr. Gu will follow us

548
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:05,300
in every operation.

549
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:12,220
Shall I make room for you?

550
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:14,140
No need. It's comfortable.

551
00:26:22,340 --> 00:26:23,540
It looks nice.

552
00:26:51,300 --> 00:26:52,300
Go on.

553
00:26:55,420 --> 00:26:56,700
Is it that guy?

554
00:26:56,700 --> 00:26:57,940
How did they find out?

555
00:26:58,460 --> 00:26:59,260
I don't know.

556
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:14,660
Hey.

557
00:27:16,180 --> 00:27:17,140
Any red wine?

558
00:27:18,500 --> 00:27:19,300
What?

559
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:23,220
Red wine.

560
00:27:29,220 --> 00:27:30,260
Red wine...

561
00:27:30,940 --> 00:27:31,980
No.

562
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:35,260
But I got something better
than red wine.

563
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:36,300
Want to try?

564
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:38,180
Mr. Gu is very skilled.

565
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:41,540
Yes, he's so natural.

566
00:27:42,140 --> 00:27:43,060
Better than you.

567
00:27:44,980 --> 00:27:45,860
It's too crowded here.

568
00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:47,060
Let's go to the back.

569
00:27:48,980 --> 00:27:49,780
Hurry up.

570
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:09,860
You got the right person.

571
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:11,620
I have nice goods.

572
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:12,340
It's really good.

573
00:28:12,460 --> 00:28:13,180
Red Dragon.

574
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:14,660
Do you have meth?

575
00:28:15,340 --> 00:28:15,820
Meth.

576
00:28:16,100 --> 00:28:17,940
Dude, that's too nice.

577
00:28:17,940 --> 00:28:18,860
I don't have it.

578
00:28:19,060 --> 00:28:20,140
But this is not bad.

579
00:28:22,780 --> 00:28:23,940
Alright, I'll take them all.

580
00:28:24,620 --> 00:28:25,060
All of them?

581
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:25,820
Yes.

582
00:28:30,540 --> 00:28:31,860
What's going on?

583
00:28:32,420 --> 00:28:33,340
Play dirty?

584
00:28:34,540 --> 00:28:36,220
You two fight me and want to use a gun?

585
00:28:36,580 --> 00:28:37,740
Forget it.

586
00:28:42,540 --> 00:28:44,420
Who is she?

587
00:28:45,740 --> 00:28:46,580
Listen.

588
00:28:46,660 --> 00:28:48,140
Go away. I don't want to hurt you.

589
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:53,660
Ouch!

590
00:28:54,140 --> 00:28:56,660
